<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="make-sure">make sure</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>弄清；查明；设法确保：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He arrived at the cinema early to <strong>make sure of</strong> a seat. 
为确保有座位，他早早地到了电影院。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>make sure</strong> (<strong>that</strong>) we take good care of students on campus. 
我们确保在校园里照顾好学生。</p><footer>译林① – 1</footer></div></div>